{
  "stem": "7093.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, the, the flat was pretty, pretty dirty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was full with very interesting mementos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He traveled around a lot in his life and did all sorts of things in his life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he was a highly intelligent man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But he, he was-- the flat was not very clean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I wanted to show my, my thankfulness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so I started cleaning the flat, which was the worst I could do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because obviously his wife [LAUGHS] didn't think it was-- it was for me to show her up, which I certainly didn't want to because I, I, I loved her.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She was lovely to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But things became very tense.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But I was anyway already looking for a job because I wanted to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I didn't want to be on their back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I was only for short while with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They said that I can stay forever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But I-- there-- it was evident that I'm not going to stay.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And then, of course, things got tense.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I got the job with [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH], French [NON-ENGLISH], had a, a children's home out in Montmorency.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Now, this children's home was run by two non-Jewish women who actually were hiding-- hid during the war 40 Jewish children whose parents were deported and whose parents didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they were-- and one of these children was a very interesting case.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "The children were between 5-- I think between 5 and 15.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And there was only one 15-year-old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And the 15-year-old was the following-- his mother was a French Jewess.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "His father was a German SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the father-- and there were rumors that the father had his mother deported to get rid of her.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
